      "title": "FUD FAQ | A Weekly Community Thread | Week 64",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "FUD FAQ | A Weekly Community Thread | Week 64"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/0*pNRKjnLp0-bu7WCq.jpeg",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Question of the Week"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "What’s happening during NFT NYC?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "So much… most people’s calendars are starting to look like tetris, wouldn’t be so bad if someone made a gamefi adaptation. If you’re going to be around DIGITALAX is hosting two locally produced events celebrating the full kick off of #cc0summer with the first public screening of an indie NFT street art film, produced by the F3M designer realm, and an incredible music x fashion gathering + open bar in the heart of the meatpacking district."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "We’ve almost reached capacity with hundreds of RSVPs already to both events… if you’re in town make sure to RSVP before tickets run out… we’d love to meet you IRL!"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Most Common Repeat Question"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "li",
          "value": "Is the entire global economy going to zero?"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Nah, don’t be silly."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Tis but a flesh wound."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Stick to the plan, stay in the game, keep building. The comprehensive economic refactoring is still underway, the web3 open metaverse awaits."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Top Controversies"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "When you try and disguise web2 with web3, the results will not be good. Sometimes the bright lights of the bull run dim and burst when the bears come to play."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "With all that said that, decentralised engineering is working just as expected."
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*34dIjA8WQw8eJ79hkqUvGQ.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*Rh8yuQE65ouGLE4qE8Hv1Q.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Silly Fails and Trolling"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Well, in hindsight, I guess it would have been nice for the foundation to drop that branding sooner …. 👀👀👀🫡"
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*PW7mvSEokmbLa3SF_YjNxg.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "View all FUD FAQ here."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "If you would like a question answered or contribute content to next weeks article please reach out through our DIGITALAX Discord server in #FUD-FAQ channel!"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Join our Community!"
        },
        {
